# Goals and Audit

## When the user asks to audit or fix the site:
1. Work through `docs/GOALS_AND_UI_AUDIT.md` checklist
2. For each failure: **fix it**, don't just report it
3. Run `npm run build` — must pass
4. Re-check affected items after fixes
5. Repeat until checklist passes and build is green

## Sources of truth
- `docs/GOALS_AND_UI_AUDIT.md` — audit checklist
- `docs/plans/master-plan.md` — implementation priority
- `CLAUDE.md` — design system

## Scope
- Run audit only on files within current task scope, not unrelated pages
- Do not stop after one pass — iterate until goals are met